A moderator's job is to keep the board neat and tidy, moving posts to their right sections and deleting posts as necessary.<br>
This is done, frankly, to free up more time for Edeina and myself, but also in a pursuit to involve more people in the future development of this board.<br>
The current command structure is simple at the moment.<br>
<br>
 -- Edeina: Main admin, absolute authority<br>
  -- Kivorn: Secondary admin, full authority<br>
<br>
The moderator would be placed right below myself in authority, with the power to move, delete and edit posts at his discretion, and would also be allowed to pick a title of his choosing, within certain limits of course.<br>
He would not have the option to edit the settings of this board.<br>
<br>
We've opted for an application based selection because we feel that a moderator, or admin for that matter, would do a better job if he's eager to get to it.<br>
In this application please list:<br>
<br>
* EZBoard handle used on this board<br>
** Why you want to be a moderator<br>
*** How you would want to make this board a better community<br>
**** Return email adress<br>
***** Characters played on Ayonae Ro<br>
<br>
What will be valued in this application is primarilly the willingness to make this board a better place, but also the nature of your previous posts (yes, I will pull a checkup on you) and seniority will have a certain impact, if not large.<br>
<br>
Send an application to: kivorn@spela.com if you feel this would be something for you.<br>
